'''''Fairy Tales: Jaina and the Hanadak''''' was a planned young readers book, to be written by [[John Whitman]] and illustrated by [[Kathy Mitchell]]. In it, [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] would try to visit the Old Forest Woman on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]], but instead encountered the carnivorous Hanadak beast.

